{"tid":256801,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]有篇古代小說搵唔返","createTime":"2017-05-24T19:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T19:58:04.000Z","uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2d73361772906a5e3113114210d17b57636c1f","tid":256801,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:35:25.000Z","msg":"印象中係出自三言兩拍定唔知聊齋<br />\n內容係講有個小官比朝廷派去嶺南上任，咁隨行人員唔知比野獸食晒定中瘴氣瓜晒，得返佢一個，跟住當地迎接既人黎救走佢<br />\n後尾搭船遇到個奇女子，自此係咁幫佢逢凶化吉，包括令當地蠱族d人服佢，唔再搞搞震<br />\n最後好似個官調返朝廷，自此同呢個女人分別咗<br />\n我知呢個故仔好冷門，但如果睇過可唔可以講我知出處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09979790b9f55f4c46ef33796d6bd9f250713ff","tid":256801,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:42:53.000Z","msg":"搵返了無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f50dbd9071a760fc734534c908ca8f28f2dd9d","tid":256801,"uid":59632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:43:07.000Z","msg":"一心草堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dbd6a94a024c03446993406bdecbc2110b0276","tid":256801,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一心草堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三言兩拍 楊謙之客舫遇俠僧"}]}